OL,7,FLess than half of victims surveyed by
OL,8,Fa watchdog were confident they could
OL,9,Fget justice by reporting a crime or
OL,10,Fthat the criminal justice system is
OL,11,Feffective, according to a report.
OL,13,FSome 6,581 people who had experienced
OL,14,Fcrime took part in the online research
OL,15,Fby the Victim's Commissioner, in the
OL,16,Flargest survey of victims conducted by
OL,17,Fthe independent body.
