OL,4,Ccriminal justice system is effective `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FThe annual survey for 2024 found 46%
OL,8,Fof participants were confident the
OL,9,Fcriminal justice system was effective
OL,10,Fwhile 42% were confident they could
OL,11,Freceive justice by reporting a crime.
OL,13,FSome 52% were also confident the
OL,14,Fcriminal justice system was fair.
OL,16,FThe report published on Thursday said
OL,17,Fthat a lack of resources, poor
OL,18,Fcommunication between agencies and
OL,19,Fsystemic biases were among the reasons
OL,20,Ffor the lack of confidence in the
OL,21,Fsystem from victims.
