OL,7,FThe findings come amid a record high
OL,8,Fcrown court backlog of cases, with
OL,9,Fsome trials being listed in 2029.
OL,11,FMinisters are due to respond this
OL,12,Fautumn to recommendations made by Sir
OL,13,FBrian Leveson to overhaul the court
OL,14,Fsystem, aimed at trying to "reduce the
OL,15,Frisk of total system collapse".
OL,17,FThe commissioner added: "Court delays
OL,18,Fremain a major source of harm,
OL,19,Fparticularly for victims of rape,
OL,20,Fsexual assault, stalking, and
OL,21,Fharassment.
