OL,7,F"These delays prolong trauma and
OL,8,Fdamage mental health."
OL,10,FThe report included more than 150
OL,11,Ftestimonies from victims who took part
OL,12,Fin the survey.
OL,14,FOne woman aged between 35-44, who was
OL,15,Fa victim of rape and sexual assault,
OL,16,Fsaid of dropping out of her case: "Too
OL,17,Fstressful, (it) took too long. It
OL,18,Fruined my life and I thought I'd lose
OL,19,Fmy family if I carried on with the
OL,20,Fcase."
