OL,7,FBaroness Newlove raised the issue of
OL,8,Faccess to support for victims as a
OL,9,F"real concern", and said when
OL,10,Freferrals did happen, people often
OL,11,F"faced long waits for under-resourced
OL,12,Fservices".
OL,14,FThe responses also showed just 14% of
OL,15,Fvictims had heard of the Victim's
OL,16,FRight to Review, which allows them the
OL,17,Fright to ask for a review of a police
OL,18,Fdecision not to charge a suspect.
